<h2>Accommodation</h2>
<p>All tours departing Gatwick &amp; Heathrow are based on 14 nights. All tours departing Manchester &amp; Glasgow are based on 13 nights.</p>
<p><strong>Vancouver                           </strong><br /><a rel="noopener noreferrer" data-udi="umb://document/4e1f479459f7486099eeeb5335cab519" href="/{localLink:umb://document/4e1f479459f7486099eeeb5335cab519}" target="_blank" title="Fairmont Waterfront">Fairmont Waterfront</a>*****<a rel="noopener noreferrer" data-udi="umb://document/05d1bf4c78b74d96977f9e993299b6d5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/05d1bf4c78b74d96977f9e993299b6d5}" target="_blank" title="Holiday Inn &amp; Suites Downtown Hotel"><br />Holiday Inn Downtown</a>****<br /><a rel="noopener noreferrer" data-udi="umb://document/05d1bf4c78b74d96977f9e993299b6d5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/05d1bf4c78b74d96977f9e993299b6d5}" target="_blank" title="Holiday Inn &amp; Suites Downtown Hotel">Holiday Inn Downtown</a>***</p>
<p><strong>Jasper </strong>                                               <br /><a rel="noopener noreferrer" data-udi="umb://document/8aac270d8d2f494788cf74d001d5694e" href="/{localLink:umb://document/8aac270d8d2f494788cf74d001d5694e}" target="_blank" title="Fairmont Jasper Park Lodge">Fairmont Jasper Park Lodge</a>*****<br /><a rel="noopener noreferrer" data-udi="umb://document/2d1776feaf4d4776a395eb9ad8e798ef" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2d1776feaf4d4776a395eb9ad8e798ef}" target="_blank" title="Sawridge Hotel">Sawridge</a>****<br /><a rel="noopener noreferrer" data-udi="umb://document/d64f704a613b4665b28b3a9de2bd58f8" href="/{localLink:umb://document/d64f704a613b4665b28b3a9de2bd58f8}" target="_blank" title="Whistlers Inn Hotel">Whistlers Inn</a>***</p>
<p><strong>Banff </strong><br /><a rel="noopener noreferrer" data-udi="umb://document/9bf71a1bae6047f189c186ca3743fe70" href="/{localLink:umb://document/9bf71a1bae6047f189c186ca3743fe70}" target="_blank" title="Fairmont Banff Springs">Fairmont Banff Springs</a>*****<br /><a rel="noopener noreferrer" data-udi="umb://document/04a1531612454a139945ef52f5d36ace" href="/{localLink:umb://document/04a1531612454a139945ef52f5d36ace}" target="_blank" title="Banff Park Lodge">Banff Park Lodge</a>****<br /><a rel="noopener noreferrer" data-udi="umb://document/3551b454285941e9810023182aac6f45" href="/{localLink:umb://document/3551b454285941e9810023182aac6f45}" target="_blank" title="Banff Inn Hotel">Banff Inn</a>***</p>
<p><strong>Kamloops</strong> 1 night     Moderate category hotel (all tours)</p>
<p><strong>Rocky Mountaineer Train<br /></strong></p>
<p><strong>Red Leaf Service </strong>is included on all tours. Features fully reclining seats, extended legroom, picture windows, information pack with detailed maps, breakfast and lunches served at your seat, complimentary snacks, tea, coffee and soft drinks, guided commentary, observation platform.</p>
<p><strong>Silver Leaf Services</strong> Enjoy delicious meals as you take in the awe-inspiring scenery through the panoramic windows of custom design single level dome coach (for Vancouver to Jasper route only).</p>
<p><strong>Gold Leaf Service</strong> Additional features include bi-level dome coach with overhead panoramic windows, alcoholic beverages, gourmet breakfast and lunch choices served in lower level dining room with full galley kitchen.</p>
<p>  <br />Tours depart weekly on Saturdays. Services of an Inghams Rep in each resort and all transfers are included. See individual resort pages for full details of hotels and attractions.</p>
